Restful Chat Server written in Play Framework utilizing GCM (google cloud messenging)
===================================== 

To setup for heroku deployment:

step 1: clone git repository
step 2: type "heroku create" to create remote branch
step 3: type "git push heroku master"
step 4: lookup database credentials on https://postgres.heroku.com/databases for the database that play just created and follow the instructions in conf/prod.conf for setting up database credentials
step 5: commit all changed files 
step 6: push to heroku with "git push heroku master"
step 7: once all files are commited successfully, type "heroku restart"
step 8: check everything is working by making a new account with curl executing this command
"curl -v -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Content-type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"username":"username","password":"password"}' http://{your_endpoint}/register"